4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course. In just 16 weeks, students learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics to become professional Data Analysts. The course covers topics like predictive modeling, algorithms (such as Decision Trees), supervised and unsupervised learning models, and industry-standard tools. Students also have the opportunity to work on real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. Classes are held three times a week with a maximum of 12 students per class. A recognized certificate is awarded upon completion. No previous experience is required, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop